overview.en: WGT is a fan member medal of the WSCF user community and community brand. It is an important part of the expansion of platform functions, the realization of multiple rights and benefits, and the return of ecological value.
overview.zh: WGT 是 WSCF旗下用户社区，社群品牌的一个粉丝会员勋章,是平台功能的拓展、多项权益的实现和生态价值回报的重要组成部分。
